survey_response.review_text: Dr. Pradeepa, you are simply a blessing! I cannot express enough gratitude for the exceptional care and support you provided during my delivery. Your compassion, professionalism and expertise made a difficult time so much easier, and I will always be grateful. Your on time reply through whatsapp messages to all our queries helped a lot during pregnancy.I would highly recommend you to any expectant mother in need of a gynecologist.  Dr. Pradeepa, thank you for being such a shining example of what a great doctor should be. Your care and support will never be forgotten, and I wish you all the best in your continued success. Keep shining!

I got my baby delivered by Dr. Pradeepa. *** ** ** ********* ******. For the very first visit I was totally satisfied with her down to earth friendly behavior and the way she treats the patients is ultimate. The best part of her is patience, open to answer as many doubts and questions, very quick response via watsapp. *** *** *** ********* *********** ***** *** *********. Overall my pregnancy journey went smooth because of her support. I glad to express my gratitude and thankfulness. I recommend those who wish to have safe and memorable experience, who expects transparency. Thank you for your guidance and support.
